        <level>
          <content>
            <table uk:widths="3.14in 3.15in">
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Affirmative procedure</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>Statutory instruments that are subject to the draft “affirmative procedure” must be approved by both the House of Commons and House of Lords to become law.</p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
