                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/commons/2020-10-15/debates/ADEDB9E4-6D5F-4445-9971-D9F239FED9BD/CovertHumanIntelligenceSources(CriminalConduct)Bill"><u>Vol. 682 Col. 563</u></a></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td colspan="3">
                  <p><i>House of Lords</i></p>
                </td>
